{{lang: TypeScript}}

# The AST barrel

`index` re-exports the AST model layer as one surface: the node foundation, the containers, line ranges, the tokens, and the wefts. Each `export *` forwards one model module, so a consumer can reach the whole model through `#ast`.

## The module {../src/ast/index.ts}

=>

export * from '@athrio/loom-core/LoomNode'
export * from './LoomAst'
export * from './LineRanges'
export * from './LoomTokens'
export * from './Weft'
